"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?31/62/32743/abstract/2\">",
"      Beers SL, Abramo TJ. Otitis externa review. Pediatr Emerg Care 2004; 20:250.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
